 gonna move\n\n[Pre-Chorus - Bass enters, tension building]\nNo need to rush\nThis game is working\nRight here with you\n\n[Chorus - Drums kick, rhythm locks, confident energy]\nWe're almost touching\nDon't cross that line\nI want this edge tonight\n\nThis slow sweet build\nOur eyes are locked\nThe waiting always wins\n\nWe circle around\nWe both just stall\nThis low burning heat\nYour move and my call\n\n[Verse 3 - Pull back, intimate]\nYour fingers graze the bar\nMine rest right next to yours\nWe could close this space\nBut we're not gonna move\n\nThe whole room fades out\nJust this small space here\nThe gap between our hands\n\n[Bridge - Strip minimal, tension held]\nLook away from me\nThen come right back\n\nThe pause still works\nThe magnetic pull\n\nLater means so much more\nJust trust this feeling\nIf we stretch this moment out\nWe both will win\n\n[Chorus - Full build, assertive groove, open dynamics]\nWe're almost touching\nDon't cross that line\nI want this edge tonight\n\nThis slow sweet build\nOur eyes are locked\nThe waiting always wins\n\nWe circle around\nWe both just stall\nThis low burning heat\nYour move and my call\n\n[Outro - Fade rhythm, sustained warmth]\nSoon but not right now\nJust stay right here\nMmm\nStay",59485472128787,"fixed",120,270,"4","en","E minor",true,2,0.85,0.9,0,0]},{"id":5,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[789.2473527323377,-431.4261775118947],"size":[520,530],"flags":{},"order":5,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{},"widgets_values":["## Model Links (for Local Users)\n\n**diffusion_models**\n\n- [acestep_v1.5_turbo.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ace_step_1.5_ComfyUI_files/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/acestep_v1.5_turbo.safetensors)\n\n**text_encoders**\n\n- [qwen_0.6b_ace15.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ace_step_1.5_ComfyUI_files/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_0.6b_ace15.safetensors)\n- [qwen_1.7b_ace15.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ace_step_1.5_C